SANYA, China - Miss India, Manushi Chhillar has won Miss World 2017.  The runners-up were Miss England, Stephanie Hill, and Miss Mexico, Andrea Meza.  African was represented in the top 5 by Miss Kenya, Magline Jeruto.  South Africa was represented by Miss SA 2017 runner-up, Ade van Heerden, who reached the top 10.  PICS: Miss SA's Miss World gown revealed eNCA